    <item>
      <title>惠誉削减了中国对财务削弱，债务问题的评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/fitch-cuts-china-rating-over-weakening-finances-debt-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级将中国的主权评级降低了对削弱财务和上涨公共债务的担忧，仅在美国对该国征收更高的关税之后的一天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/fitch-cuts-china-rating-over-weakening-finances-debt-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 13:05:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>破坏特拉菲格拉的瑞士总检察长想要我们式的力量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/swiss-attorney-general-who-busted-trafigura-wants-us-style-prosecution-powers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士的最高检察官呼吁立法者赋予他清除美国风格的权力和更多调查人员，以使更快地向错误的公司伸张正义。尽管他承认这个想法可能需要数年的时间才能成为法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/swiss-attorney-general-who-busted-trafigura-wants-us-style-prosecution-powers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
